{"tid":2011632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"和你Shop新形式——較鬧鐘播《願榮光》","createTime":"2020-05-11T06:36:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T05:40:57.000Z","uid":309398,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4d4d3c21dfffa769a282cde88d0e1cc25ffe56a5","tid":2011632,"uid":309398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:36:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">其實係巴打提出嘅，但我覺得個idea好好，所以我拾人牙慧。</span></span><br />\n點解要用呢種方法？<br />\n其實唔少和理非會因為商場<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冇得blackblock 以及班狗太早進駐</span></span>而打退堂鼓，而較左鬧鐘就可以同一時間準時開始，大大增加效率。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">以前你眼望我眼，估吓係咪手足</span></span>，拖五至十分鐘，今次順其自然夠鐘就開波<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「班狗唔會理你有冇唱歌，總之就會ss你」</span></span><br />\n冇錯，但呢樣野係無法避免嘅。諗番轉頭佢如果因為咁捉人，咁個場面會太肉酸，你個藍絲老母見你因為響鬧鐘而比人拉都會轉黃啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而開始咗都冇狗咪<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">慢慢跟住唱囉</span></span><br />\n<br />\n總之用鬧鐘作為開始訊號係最<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">冇先兆、有效率</span></span>嘅"},{"pid":"3b91e43839516cdad39942f59bde4c182d706bc5","tid":2011632,"uid":62799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:38:06.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"62c69d0016204b8bbfb3b4cb6a957d24a6da8bd3","tid":2011632,"uid":309398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b91e43839516cdad39942f59bde4c182d706bc5","tid":2011632,"uid":62799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:38:06.000Z","msg":"推一推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:38:21.000Z","msg":"Thanks <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"283d817599cd6d1fd71da036e3a27b618ce7acd7","tid":2011632,"uid":2526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:39:28.000Z","msg"